# Copy to .env for LOCAL TESTING ONLY and fill in. NEVER commit the real .env,
# and NEVER bake it into the image — the judging harness injects all three of
# these at runtime and the submitted container must read them from the
# environment (Participant Guide, Track 1).
FIREWORKS_API_KEY=fw_your_key_here
FIREWORKS_BASE_URL=https://api.fireworks.ai/inference/v1
# Comma-separated permitted model ids — the OFFICIAL Track 1 allowed list
# (organizer announcement, 2026-07-08). The harness-injected value always
# wins over anything written here. Local-testing note: Gemma models are
# on-demand on Fireworks — a 404 means "not deployed on your account", not
# "banned"; the router falls through to the next tier automatically.
# (Deploying Gemma 4 E4B bills ~$7/h even when idle — undeploy after testing.)
ALLOWED_MODELS=accounts/fireworks/models/minimax-m3,accounts/fireworks/models/kimi-k2p7-code,accounts/fireworks/models/gemma-4-31b-it,accounts/fireworks/models/gemma-4-26b-a4b-it,accounts/fireworks/models/gemma-4-31b-it-nvfp4
